{"tid":844901,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【都市閒情玩完 主持會驚無工開？】其實個個非富則貴 賺錢買花戴","createTime":"2018-10-02T08:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T10:22:52.000Z","uid":54870,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"50f4fedd020c3e871e583493a862d6fcb4c49d78","tid":844901,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20181001/2_627783_0/-%E9%83%BD%E5%B8%82%E9%96%92%E6%83%85%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%8C-%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%83%E9%A9%9A%E7%84%A1%E5%B7%A5%E9%96%8B-%E5%85%B6%E5%AF%A6%E5%80%8B%E5%80%8B%E9%9D%9E%E5%AF%8C%E5%89%87%E8%B2%B4-%E8%B3%BA%E9%8C%A2%E8%B2%B7%E8%8A%B1%E6%88%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F2_627783_0%2F-%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%25B8%2582%25E9%2596%2592%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%25AE%258C-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%25A9%259A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E9%2596%258B-%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2580%258B%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25AF%258C%25E5%2589%2587%25E8%25B2%25B4-%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E9%258C%25A2%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%258A%25B1%25E6%2588%25B4&d=kQFAM6terdWJr1P%2FpqNKgARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=88562488\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F2_627783_0%2F-%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%25B8%2582%25E9%2596%2592%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%25AE%258C-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%25A9%259A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E9%2596%258B-%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2580%258B%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25AF%258C%25E5%2589%2587%25E8%25B2%25B4-%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E9%258C%25A2%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%258A%25B1%25E6%2588%25B4&h=eac688ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20181001/2_627783_0/-%E9%83%BD%E5%B8%82%E9%96%92%E6%83%85%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%8C-%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%83%E9%A9%9A%E7%84%A1%E5%B7%A5%E9%96%8B-%E5%85%B6%E5%AF%A6%E5%80%8B%E5%80%8B%E9%9D%9E%E5%AF%8C%E5%89%87%E8%B2%B4-%E8%B3%BA%E9%8C%A2%E8%B2%B7%E8%8A%B1%E6%88%B4</a><br />\n<br />\n大王安德尊，佢係<span style=\"color: gold;\">元朗地王</span>，咁多年嚟買唔少地皮起屋，又炒埋地產，加上一直傳佢有好龐大嘅家族生意，喺加拿大都大把樓，做主持真係興趣嚟㗎咋！<br />\n<br />\n另外就係宋芝齡，中韓混血嘅佢被喻為「韓國通」，10年前佢食正韓風吹起，每次有韓星來港大台都一定派佢出動。之後順勢開韓國語言學校，而家<span style=\"color: gold;\">每個月有成6位數字嘅收入</span>，係喺大台搵到嘅10倍！據聞出年更會擴充到六間學校。嚟緊仲會搞埋韓國投資移民添，真係泛泛都撈得掂！<br />\n<br />\n而姚嘉妮同樣有自己嘅生意，2013年佢同老公林祖輝搞童裝生意，而家已經有成6間分店，仲透露過想上市，可見佢賺唔少啦！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">老貓最愛嘅</span></span>彭慧中，有傳佢屋企喺香港大陸都有幾間廠，一家住三千呎康樂園獨立屋。<br />\n<br />\n連知名度最低嘅蘇晉霆，原來本身就係有錢仔，家族物業逾4,000萬，喺大台一向唔算多野撈，但就住緊半山區900幾呎豪宅。父幹真係好重要㗎！"},{"pid":"24829bb4d441d0be99f3d6bb25f05c42f507b61d","tid":844901,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4919446ab8034ff8574026d1d6be4a366226e19","tid":844901,"uid":54870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/163550_a3e593c57f2fda7c38fb6dc265550a55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F163550_a3e593c57f2fda7c38fb6dc265550a55.jpg&h=d942eae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/163627_326a9c2219c8cc0a24b2eef574b28137.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F163627_326a9c2219c8cc0a24b2eef574b28137.gif&h=4e6cc602&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1e9cd1833cf7101603f1c435a56b251eb091d3c","tid":844901,"uid":54870,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/163754_b1d2904